<p>The Sport for All Day events took place on April 12th, at Praça do Tap Seac, receiving great support from the public in a welcoming atmosphere.</p>The organizers hope that by organizing the "Sport for All Day", public participation in regular sport and adherence to a healthy life style will improve. <p>"Sport for All Day" events will continue to be held monthly in public places, hoping to promote interest in and love of sports. </p>Learn more <a href="http://www.sport.gov.mo/pt/news?id=2624">here </a>(original content in Portuguese)<p></p>